+<h1>IDE Features</h1>
+<p>At present the core features include the following:
+	<ul>
+		<li>C# Text Editor with Code Completion</li>
+		<li>Debugger</li>
+		<li>Help Integration</li>
+		<li>Gtk# Forms Designer</li>
+	</ul>
+</p>
